{"tid":2262770,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"美國國務院譴責本港警方拘捕鍾翰林等三人","createTime":"2020-10-29T10:45:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-29T13:21:56.000Z","uid":240362,"like":72,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"861de04f62806f98ba865691cc0a0f64bd91f554","tid":2262770,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T10:45:35.000Z","msg":"前學生動源召集人鍾翰林被控分裂國家、串謀發布煽動性刊物等罪，還押至明年1月再審訊。<br />\n<br />\n美國國務院回覆查詢表示，讉責香港警方拘捕及扣留鍾翰林等3名學生民主社運人士，指警方國安處人員在咖啡室拘捕一名青年，是應該受到讉責。<br />\n<br />\n發言人表示，《港區國安法》繼續被用作壓制異議，削減港人個人自由，而非用作確保安全，又說香港當權者持續用執法達到政治目的，是違反法治，亦不尊重和平集會及言論自由的權利。<br />\n<br />\n早前有報道指，鍾翰林被捕前曾到美國駐港澳總領事館尋求政治庇護。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1557328-20201029.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1557328-20201029.htm&d=2u41qa%2Bce9Gslgrzp%2F5KipB82cw%2Bhl0zMn8EQHxvzrU%3D&h=9525e56f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1557328-20201029.htm&h=c00fc9de\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1557328-20201029.htm</a>"},{"pid":"a116b29fdfd261171198952bdd41cf1f260beeac","tid":2262770,"uid":103965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T10:45:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6069933c490edada2ee71ad46172e44108dcc18f","tid":2262770,"uid":103965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T10:46:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img s